// src/components/Header.js
import React from 'react';
import { Box, Flex, Heading, Link, Spacer, UnorderedList, ListItem } from '@chakra-ui/react';

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <Flex
      as="header"
      align="center"
      justify="space-between"
      bgColor="teal.500"
      color="white"
      p="4"
      mb="8"
    >
      <Box>
        <Heading as="h1" size="md">
          Seu Nome
        </Heading>
      </Box>
      <Spacer />
      <UnorderedList listStyleType="none" display="flex" justifyContent="space-around">
        <ListItem cursor="pointer" fontWeight="bold">
          <Link href="#about">Sobre Mim</Link>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem cursor="pointer" fontWeight="bold">
          <Link href="#projects">Projetos</Link>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem cursor="pointer" fontWeight="bold">
          <Link href="#contact">Contato</Link>
        </ListItem>
      </UnorderedList>
    </Flex>
  );
};

export default Header;
